@node "Command Quit" "MegaD v3.1 - by John L. Jones"

'Quit' command  &  @{" Menu Project " link "Menu Project"} / 'Quit' menu item:
====================================================

When selected, this command will exit MegaD.  This command
is comparable to selecting the MegaD window's close gadget.


