command allowing you to utilize AmigaDOS's pattern matching features
will utilize this window.

Notice the text in the upper portion of the pattern match window.
This is designed to act as a reminder of the different types of
patterns you can use.  Acceptable patterns will be discussed in
the pattern match window's string gadget section.


