The 'Menus & Devices' preference windows really combines two completely
unrelated items into one window.


   Top half of the window:
   ======================

   The top half of the window lists an abbreviated view of the
   @{"program control windows" link "Program Control Window 1"} for @{"user defined Utiltity Menu items" link "User Defined Menus"}.
   

   
   Bottom half of the window:
   =========================
   
   The bottom half of the window lists the logical and physical
   @{"devices" link "Device Gadgets"} which can be attached to the nine device gadgets in
   the MegaD main window.



