@node "User Defined Menus" "MegaD v3.1 - by John L. Jones"

User Defined Menus:
==================

MegaD's allows you to define the first 5 items of the @{"Utilities" link "Menu Utilities}
menu.  We'll call these five items a "set" of user defined menus.

Even better, MegaD allows you to define more than one set of
5 menu items for the @{"Utilities menu" link "Menu Utilities"}.  You can select which
set of 5 items is displayed in the menu using the menu items:

   @{" Utilities " link "Menu Utilities"} / @{" Next Menu Set  " link "Menu Utilities - Next Menu Set"}
   @{" Utilities " link "Menu Utilities"} / @{" Prev Menu Set  " link "Menu Utilities - Prev Menu Set"}
   @{" Utilities " link "Menu Utilities"} / @{" First Menu Set " link "Menu Utilities - First Menu Set"}
   @{" Utilities " link "Menu Utilities"} / @{" Last Menu Set  " link "Menu Utilities - Last Menu Set"}
   
Use MegaD's @{"Menus & Devices preferences" link "Prefs Menus & Devices"} to define menu sets.



See Also:   @{" Keypads - Menu Sets " link "Prefs Keypads - Menu Sets"} preference window
            @{" Menus & Devices     " link "Prefs Menus & Devices"} preference window
            @{" Menu Sets           " link "Menu Sets"} discussion
            @{" Utilities           " link "Menu Utilities"} menu
            @{" Menu Utilities " link "Menu Utilities"} / @{" User Menu Items 1-5 " link "Menu Utilities - User Menu Items 1-5"} menu items

@endnode

@node "PMD - LhA" "MegaD v3.1 - by John L. Jones"

@{" Prefs Menus & Devices " link "Prefs Menus & Devices"} - LhA, Arc, LhArc, Next & Prev:
======================================================

 --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|        @{"  LhA  " link "PMD - LhA"} @{"  Arc  " link "PMD - LhA"} @{" LhArc " link "PMD - LhA"} @{"  Next  " link "PMD - LhA"} @{"  Prev  " link "PMD - LhA"} @{"  Add  " link "PMD - Add"} @{" Delete " link "PMD - Delete"}   Menu Sets  |
|        Menu Title    Program Name   Flags           Append at end              |
| Menu 1 @{"             " link "Prefs M&D - Menu 1-5"} @{"              " link "Prefs M&D - Menu 1-5"} @{"               " link "Prefs M&D - Menu 1-5"} @{"             " link "Prefs M&D - Menu 1-5"} @{" Control... " link "Prefs M&D - Control"} |



The first 5 (out of 7) button gadgets on the top row of the
@{"Menus & Devices Preferences Window" link "Prefs Menus & Devices"} merely select which menu
set is displayed in the window.

MegaD's default configuration includes three separate menu
sets...<LhA>, <Arc> and <LhArc>.

Selecting the following gadget accomplishes the following:

   <LhA>    Loads the first menu set into the @{"Menus & Devices" link "Prefs Menus & Devices"}
            preferences window (under MegaD's default config,
            LhA is the first menu set).
   
   <Arc>    Loads the second menu set into the @{"Menus & Devices" link "Prefs Menus & Devices"}
            preferences window (under MegaD's default config,
            Arc is the first menu set).
   
   <LhArc>  Loads the third menu set into the @{"Menus & Devices" link "Prefs Menus & Devices"}
            preferences window (under MegaD's default config,
            LhArc is the first menu set).
   
   <Next>   Loads the next menu set into the @{"Menus & Devices" link "Prefs Menus & Devices"}
            preferences window.
   
   <Prev>   Loads the previous menu set into the @{"Menus & Devices" link "Prefs Menus & Devices"}
            preferences window.


See Also:   @{" Keypads - Menu Sets " link "Prefs Keypads - Menu Sets"} preference window
            @{" Menus & Devices     " link "Prefs Menus & Devices"} preference window
            @{" User Defined Menus  " link "User Defined Menus"} discussion
