===========================================

The <View Text Tab Width> is used to specify the number of blank
spaces that MegaD's text viewer should use for a <TAB> character.


See Also:   @{" Miscellaneous     " link "Prefs Miscellaneous"} preferences window
            @{" View Text         " link "Command View Text"} built-in command
