to be.

Immediately to the right of the <Gadgets Down > integer gadget,
MegaD lists the minimum and maximum acceptable values for  
<Gadgets Down>.  These values are based upon your entry in the
@{"Inner Window Height" link "Gadget Set - Inner Window Height"} gadget.


See Also:   @{" Gadget Set                  " link "Gadget Set Window"} definition window
            @{" Gadget Set - Gadgets Across " link "Gadget Set - Gadgets Across"} definition
