@node "Menu Utilities - User Menu Items 1-5" "MegaD v3.1 - by John L. Jones"

@{" Menu Utilities " link "Menu Utilities"} / User Menu Items 1-5:
======================================

The top 5 items in the Utilities Menu are user dependent.  MegaD
provides defaults for these menu items, but allows you to alter
them to suit your needs.

Additionally, the first 5 items of the Utilities Menu are called
a "user menu set".  You can define more than one "set" of 5 user
menu items.  After defining these sets, you can use the following
menu items to select the desired "user menu set":

   @{"Utilities" link "Menu Utilities"} / @{"First Menu Set" link "Menu Utilities - First Menu Set"}
   @{"Utilities" link "Menu Utilities"} / @{"Prev Menu Set " link "Menu Utilities - Prev Menu Set"}
   @{"Utilities" link "Menu Utilities"} / @{"Next Menu Set " link "Menu Utilities - Next Menu Set"}
   @{"Utilities" link "Menu Utilities"} / @{"Last Menu Set " link "Menu Utilities - Last Menu Set"}


Default Menu Sets:
=================

   MegaD provides 3 default menu sets.  They are:
   
   Menu Set 1:       Menu Set 2:       Menu Set 3:
   ==========        ==========        ==========
   LhA Pack          Arc Pack          LhArc Pack
   LhA Unpack        Arc Unpack        LhArc Unpack
   LhA List          Arc List          LhArc List
   LhA Text          Type File2        Type File3
   LhA Recursive     Edit File2        Edit File3
   
   These menu sets are for use with the popular archiving utilities
   <LhA>, <Arc> and <LhArc>.  If you don't use these archiving
   programs, don't worry.  MegaD has included them as defaults
   merely because many people DO use them.


Altering / Adding Menu Sets:
===========================

   MegaD allows you to alter existing menu sets, and even to add
   new menu sets (thereby resulting in more than 3 menu sets).
   
   To do so, use the MegaD @{"Menus & Devices preference area" link "Prefs Menus & Devices"}.


See Also:   @{" Utilities " link "Menu Utilities"} / @{" First Menu Set " link "Menu Utilities - First Menu Set"} menu item
            @{" Utilities " link "Menu Utilities"} / @{" Prev Menu Set  " link "Menu Utilities - Prev Menu Set"} menu item
            @{" Utilities " link "Menu Utilities"} / @{" Next Menu Set  " link "Menu Utilities - Next Menu Set"} menu item
            @{" Utilities " link "Menu Utilities"} / @{" Last Menu Set  " link "Menu Utilities - Last Menu Set"} menu item
            @{" Menus & Devices " link "Prefs Menus & Devices"} preferences

@endnode

