@node "Menu Show - All" "MegaD v3.1 - by John L. Jones"

@{" Menu Show " link "Menu Show"} / All:
=================

When you select <Show / All>, MegaD will include all of the following
inside directory windows (in addition to filenames & directory names):

   File size.
   Date & time the file was created.
   File protection bits.
   File comment.

As a matter of fact, selecting the <Show / All> menu item is merely
a shortcut for selecting all of the following menu items:

   @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Size       " link "Menu Show - Size"}
   @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Date       " link "Menu Show - Date"}
   @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Protection " link "Menu Show - Protection"}
   @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Comment    " link "Menu Show - Comment"}

If you select <Show / All>, and not all windows reflect the change,
select @{"Show" link "Menu Show"} / @{"Reset All" link "Menu Show - Reset All"} to force the change.


See Also:   @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" None       " link "Menu Show - None"} menu item
            @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Size       " link "Menu Show - Size"} menu item
            @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Date       " link "Menu Show - Date"} menu item
            @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Protection " link "Menu Show - Protection"} menu item
            @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Comment    " link "Menu Show - Comment"} menu item
            @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Reset All  " link "Menu Show - Reset All"} menu item

@endnode

@node "Menu Show - None" "MegaD v3.1 - by John L. Jones"

@{" Menu Show " link "Menu Show"} / None:
==================

When you select <Show / None>, the only item displayed inside directory
windows will be file and directory names.  MegaD WILL NOT include any
of the following;

   File size.
   Date & time the file was created.
   File protection bits.
   File comment.

As a matter of fact, selecting the <Show / None> menu item is merely
a shortcut for deselecting all of the following menu items:

   @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Size       " link "Menu Show - Size"}
   @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Date       " link "Menu Show - Date"}
   @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Protection " link "Menu Show - Protection"}
   @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Comment    " link "Menu Show - Comment"}

If you select <Show / None>, and not all windows reflect the change,
select @{"Show" link "Menu Show"} / @{"Reset All" link "Menu Show - Reset All"} to force the change.


See Also:   @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" All        " link "Menu Show - All"} menu item
            @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Size       " link "Menu Show - Size"} menu item
            @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Date       " link "Menu Show - Date"} menu item
            @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Protection " link "Menu Show - Protection"} menu item
            @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Comment    " link "Menu Show - Comment"} menu item
            @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" Reset All  " link "Menu Show - Reset All"} menu item

@endnode

@node "Menu Show - Size" "MegaD v3.1 - by John L. Jones"

@{" Menu Show " link "Menu Show"} / Size:
==================

The <Show / Size> menu item is a toggle switch, which determines whether
or not file sizes will be displayed inside @{"directory windows" link "Directory Windows"}.

If you select <Show / Size>, and not all windows reflect the change,
select @{"Show" link "Menu Show"} / @{"Reset All" link "Menu Show - Reset All"} to force the change.


See Also:   @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" All        " link "Menu Show - All"} menu item
