@node "Menu Show - Date" "MegaD v3.1 - by John L. Jones"

@{" Menu Show " link "Menu Show"} / Date:
==================

The <Show / Date> menu item is a toggle switch, which determines
whether or not file creation dates and times will be displayed
inside @{"directory windows" link "Directory Windows"}.

If you select <Show / Date>, and not all windows reflect the change,
select @{"Show" link "Menu Show"} / @{"Reset All" link "Menu Show - Reset All"} to force the change.


See Also:   @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" All        " link "Menu Show - All"} menu item
