@endnode

@node "Menu Show - Protection" "MegaD v3.1 - by John L. Jones"

@{" Menu Show " link "Menu Show"} / Protection:
========================

The <Show / Protection> menu item is a toggle switch, which
determines whether or not file protection bits will be displayed
inside @{"directory windows" link "Directory Windows"}.

If you select <Show / Protection>, and not all windows reflect the
change, select @{"Show" link "Menu Show"} / @{"Reset All" link "Menu Show - Reset All"} to force the change.


See Also:   @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" All        " link "Menu Show - All"} menu item
