@node "Menu Show - Comment" "MegaD v3.1 - by John L. Jones"

@{" Menu Show " link "Menu Show"} / Comment:
=====================

The <Show / Comment> menu item is a toggle switch, which determines whether
or not file comments will be displayed inside @{"directory windows" link "Directory Windows"}.

If you select <Show / Comment>, and not all windows reflect the change,
select @{"Show" link "Menu Show"} / @{"Reset All" link "Menu Show - Reset All"} to force the change.


