@node "Menu Show - Sort On" "MegaD v3.1 - by John L. Jones"

@{" Menu Show " link "Menu Show"} / Sort On:
=====================

The <Show / Sort On> menu item allows you to specify what parameter
MegaD should sort the contents of @{"directory windows" link "Directory Windows"} upon.

MegaD allows the following options:

   - None       (no sort)
   - Name       (filename)
   - Size       (file size)
   - Date       (file creation date/time)
   - Protection (file protection bits)
   - Comment    (file comment)
   - Extension  (file extension)


See Also:   @{" Set Protect  " link "Command Set Protect"} built-in command
            @{" File Comment " link "Command File Comment"} built-in command

@endnode

@node "Menu Show - Reset All" "MegaD v3.1 - by John L. Jones"

@{" Menu Show " link "Menu Show"} / Reset All:
=======================

When you change the attributes for the display of the
@{"directory windows" link "Directory Windows"}, only @{"DEST" link "Dest Gadget"} windows will automatically
show the change.  If you wish to reset all open
@{"directory windows" link "Directory Windows"} to reflect the current display options,
select <Show / Reset All>.


See Also:   @{" Show " link "Menu Show"} / @{" All        " link "Menu Show - All"} menu item
