@node "Menu Output - W-Tree Lines" "MegaD v3.1 - by John L. Jones"

@{" Menu Output " link "Menu Output"} / W-Tree Lines:
============================

The <Output / W-Tree Lines> menu item is designed to be used in
conjunction with:

      @{" Output File " link "Command Output File"} built-in command
      @{" Output Prt  " link "Command Output Prt"} built-in command
      @{" Output " link "Menu Output"} / @{" Output File    " link "Command Output File"} menu item
      @{" Output " link "Menu Output"} / @{" Output Printer " link "Command Output Prt"} menu item

The above commands allow you to create a record of all the files and
directories contained on your system.  You can choose to create this
record using tree lines by selecting <Output / W-Tree Lines>.

Example:    Without Tree-Lines:
            ==================
            
               Work:
                   Work:Games
                       Work:Games/Solitaire
                           .info               SolitaireHighScores
                           Solitaire           Solitaire.info
                       Work:Games/Tetris
                           .info               Tetris
                           BestScores          Tetris.info
                Games.info
            
            
            With Tree-Lines:
            ===============
            
               Work:
                |--Work:Games
                |   |--Work:Games/Solitaire
                |   |   |--.info               Solitaire High Scores
                |   |   |--Solitaire           Solitaire.info
                |   |--Work:Games/Tetris
                |   |   |--.info               Tetris
                |   |   |--BestScores          Tetris.info
                |--Games.info
            

See Also:   @{" Output File " link "Command Output File"} built-in command
            @{" Output Prt  " link "Command Output Prt"} built-in command
            @{" Output " link "Menu Output"} / @{" Output File    " link "Command Output File"} menu item
            @{" Output " link "Menu Output"} / @{" Output Printer " link "Command Output Prt"} menu item

@endnode

